graph LR
    NotebookController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-1295]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|required| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22.0+]
    NotebookController -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|optional<br/>metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    NotebookController -.->|optional<br/>USE_ISTIO=true| Istio[Istio Service Mesh]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|creates VirtualService| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>VirtualService CRD]
    NotebookController -.->|consumed by| Dashboard[Kubeflow Dashboard<br/>Notebook CRD API]

    %% Managed Resources
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| StatefulSets[StatefulSets<br/>apps/v1]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| Services[Services<br/>ClusterIP]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| VirtualServices[VirtualServices<br/>networking.istio.io]
    NotebookController -->|watches| NotebookCRs[Notebook CRDs<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]

    %% Workload Dependencies
    StatefulSets -->|creates| NotebookPods[Jupyter Notebook Pods<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]
    NotebookController -->|queries /api/kernels| NotebookPods

    %% Certificate Management (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|webhook certs<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS certificates]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|UI management| NotebookCRs
    Services -->|routes traffic| NotebookPods

